Grammy&#039;s Greatest Moments, Vol. 3 Review

07/13/2005 5:42 AM, AMG

Grammy&#039;s Greatest Moments, Vol. 3 continues the series of performances taken directly from the annual awards show, with this volume featuring performances from throughout the &#039;70s and &#039;80s. Among the artists present are Aretha Franklin, Kenny Rogers, Christopher Cross, Los Lobos, Bonnie Raitt, Joe Cocker, Olivia Newton-John, Suzanne Vega, Kenny Loggins, and Don McLean, plus more. ~ Steve Huey, All Music Guide
